column5: Hey Larry, Got your new email. How you doing? I'm not going to Canada any more. Had enough-over 60 trips. Take good care, Dennis.
Good to hear from you Dennis. I suspect you do a lot of fishing now where you live in Eagle River Area of Wisconsin Take Care Larry Schroeder
60 trips!your just getting warmed up with 60 trips under your belt.
Right! This depressed me and was not even my message.
Walleye2242 Don't Be depressed I'm going on 3 trips to Canada this Year and maybe an Alaskan trip. Larry S
I love this!!! where ya headed in Canada? I will be back in gullrock in Sept. Trying for a june/july trip to Pashkakogan.
Nice! Alaska is AWESOME too! Brett
You are definitely someone I would love to sit around a campfire with and listen to all your stories.
